@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.13 * v1)
    v2 = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.74 / tmp + 0.65) / (v2 + 0.11 * v2 + 0.83)))
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.abs(v2 + 0.86) * wp.cos(tmp + 0.09)))
    v2 = (0.56 * 0.46)
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.abs((tmp + 0.35 + v0 + 0.46)))
    v2 = tmp
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.sin(tmp + 0.97)))
    v1 = 0.68
    data[tid] = v0
